v0.8.2 (25th July 2009)
- Add GBIP::Title#to_hash()

v0.8.1 (11th June 2009)
- Fix parsing of API responses that contain multiple results
- small update to specs

v0.8.0 (7th November 2008)
- Add checks for additional error codes, and raise an appropriate error
- overhauled specs

v0.7.1 (14th October 2008)
- Correctly parse API responses that contain a # in their data
- Use ISBN13s in queries. No change to user API (we accept ISBN10s or ISBN13s)

v0.7 (2nd October 2008)
- Moved out of the RBook namespace
- Added GBIP::Title#to_yaml
- Update to using the version 3 protocol
  - extra return data (including subjects and publication country)

v0.6 (6th June 2008)
- Added support for a timeout option in case the server takes too long to respond

v0.5 (3rd July 2007)
- Initial Release
